# Therapy Insight — environment variables
#
# This app is local-first and requires NO build-time environment variables.
# It runs entirely in the browser with no backend and no accounts.
#
# Demo mode (the default) works fully offline with sample data and needs no keys.
#
# Optional cloud AI providers (OpenAI / Anthropic) are stubbed in this version.
# When you enable one in Settings, the API key is entered in the app and stored
# ONLY in your browser's localStorage on your device. It is never read from a
# .env file, never bundled into the build, and never committed to git.
#
# This file exists to document that there is nothing secret to configure here.
# If you later add a backend proxy for AI calls, put its (non-secret) public URL
# below using Vite's required VITE_ prefix, e.g.:
#
# VITE_AI_PROXY_URL=https://example.com/api/ai
